I wish I could write a
report about a subject that's

15
00:00:51,240 --> 00:00:52,760
more inspiring than that.

16
00:00:58,240 --> 00:01:00,000
I just know you're
going to excel,

17
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:02,040
and best of luck in the future.

18
00:01:02,040 --> 00:01:06,920
Most sincerely,
Layfon W. Alseif.

19
00:01:06,920 --> 00:01:10,360
Since when has he been able
to write so eloquently?

20
00:01:10,360 --> 00:01:11,560
[SNIFF]

