00:01:20,320 --> 00:01:23,120
Are you OK?

26
00:01:23,120 --> 00:01:23,920
No.

27
00:01:23,920 --> 00:01:24,800
You scared me.

28
00:01:24,800 --> 00:01:26,720
You shouldn't startle
people like that.

29
00:01:26,720 --> 00:01:28,560
My apologies, miss,
but there's something

30
00:01:28,560 --> 00:01:29,800
I need to talk with you about.

31
00:01:29,800 --> 00:01:30,800
With me?

32
00:01:30,800 --> 00:01:31,600
Yes.

33
00:01:31,600 --> 00:01:33,600
But before we go any further,
let me assure you that I

34
00:01:33,600 --> 00:01:35,240
am not trying to pick you up.

35
00:01:35,240 --> 00:01:36,880
Why would you even
say something like that?

36
00:01:36,880 --> 00:01:38,080
Because most
girls are thinking

37
00:01:38,080 --> 00:01:39,240
that when I approach them.

38
00:01:39,240 --> 00:01:40,400
I just figured you would too.

39
00:01:40,400 --> 00:01:42,200
Pretty overconfident,
aren't you?

40
00:01:42,200 --> 00:01:43,160
Do you really think so?

41
00:01:43,160 --> 00:01:44,720
Because people have
told me that before,

42
00:01:44,720 --> 00:01:47,600
but I don't have a clue where
they're getting it from.

43
00:01:47,600 --> 00:01:48,560
Huh?

44
00:01:48,560 --> 00:01:49,520
What's going on?

45
00:01:54,080 --> 00:01:58,080
Wait, is this‐‐ it's the roof.

46
00:01:58,080 --> 00:02:00,040
I was taking care of
things nice and quiet

47
00:02:00,040 --> 00:02:01,720
like, so why did you have
to go and screw it up?

48
00:02:01,720 --> 00:02:04,480
Because time is too crucial
for you to waste it talking.

49
00:02:04,480 --> 00:02:07,120
But we were ordered to
be discreet about this.

50
00:02:07,120 --> 00:02:09,840
Using your power is
anything but that, Lintens.

51
00:02:09,840 --> 00:02:13,280
Wait, did he say‐‐

52
00:02:13,280 --> 00:02:15,320
both of you are Heaven's Blades.

53
00:02:15,320 --> 00:02:18,240
You're Savaris and you're
Lintens, aren't you?

54
00:02:18,240 --> 00:02:20,560
What you want with me?

55
00:02:20,560 --> 00:02:23,080
[THEME MUSIC]

56
00:03:59,400 --> 00:04:00,480
Fon‐Fon.

57
00:04:00,480 --> 00:04:01,640
FELLI (VOICEOVER):
They're coming.

58
00:04:01,640 --> 00:04:03,480
One from the front,
one from the back.

59
00:04:03,480 --> 00:04:04,320
Got it.

60
00:04:04,320 --> 00:04:05,200
Thanks, Felli.

61
00:04:05,200 --> 00:04:06,160
So two, huh?

62
00:04:06,160 --> 00:04:07,680
How do you wanna
deal with both of them?

63
00:04:07,680 --> 00:04:10,560
Well, I'll leave them to
you while the rest of us

64
00:04:10,560 --> 00:04:12,000
